snippet: At least one rocket fired from the Egyptian Sinai peninsula struck Israel’s southern resort city of Eilat Thursday, causing alarm but no injuries,
abstract: At least one rocket fired from the Sinai Peninsula in Egypt strikes the southern Israeli resort city of Eilat, causing alarm but no injuries.
